com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.kit.editor

Enum EditorController.EditAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EditorController.EditAction>
      • com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.kit.editor.EditorController.EditAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<EditorController.EditAction>
    Enclosing class:
    EditorController

    public static enum EditorController.EditAction
extends java.lang.Enum<EditorController.EditAction>
    An 'edit' action is an action which modifies the document associated to this editor. It makes the document dirty and pushes a new item on the undo/redo stack.
